<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />You will not be afraid of terror in the night,</para>

<para style="q1">or of the arrow that flies by day,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />or of the plague that roams around in the darkness,</para>

<para style="q1">or of the disease that comes at noontime.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />A thousand may fall at your side</para>

<para style="q1">and ten thousand at your right hand,</para>

<para style="q1">but it will not reach you.</para>
